### 请求 /cps/order/page 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/order/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/order/page 接口 => 按平台筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/order/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&platformCode=taobao
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/order/page 接口 => 按会员+订单状态筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/order/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&memberId=1001&orderStatus=received
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/order/page 接口 => 按平台订单号搜索
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/order/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&platformOrderId=TEST_TB_20260102_002
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/order/page 接口 => 按时间段筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/order/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&createTime[0]=2026-01-01 00:00:00&createTime[1]=2026-12-31 23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/order/get 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/order/get?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/order/sync 接口 => 成功（手动同步淘宝最近2小时订单）
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/order/sync?platformCode=taobao&hours=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/order/sync 接口 => 成功（手动同步京东最近6小时订单）
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/order/sync?platformCode=jd&hours=6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/order/sync 接口 => 成功（手动同步拼多多最近1小时订单）
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/order/sync?platformCode=pdd&hours=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}
